      "content": "that makes sense. but i feel like some people say the \"crushing rivals\" part is kinda exaggerated because users actually like these platforms. do you think the current investigations are actually based on solid legal ground or is it more about the government just trying to assert control over companies that have become more powerful than some countries?",
